      "content": "wait, appendicitis?? that sounds way too intense. i really dont think i need a hospital, i can barely walk to the mailbox lol. i'm sure it's just a digestive thing. if i take the codeine it'll just dull the feeling so i can sleep through it. can i take like two of the codeine pills at once to make sure it actually works? i dont want to be awake in an hour feeling this.",
